  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 200°C and grease a baking dish.",
    "Toss diced sweet potato, sliced carrot, sliced onion, and chickpeas with olive oil, oregano, thyme, salt, and half the nutritional yeast.",
    "Spread vegetables evenly in the dish and roast for 25 minutes.",
    "Sauté spinach until wilted in a small pan.",
    "Remove dish from oven, stir in wilted spinach and remaining nutritional yeast, and return to oven for 10 more minutes.",
    "Let rest 5 minutes before serving."
